Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.72,0:02:21.90,OP TL,,0,0,0,,Fetelor, distrați-vă!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.88,0:02:01.93,OP,,0,0,0,,daremo jibun no ibasho wakannakunattari shite
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.37,0:02:05.79,OP,,0,0,0,,samayoutte aruku no
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.00,0:02:07.15,OP,,0,0,0,,sounan desu
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.22,0:02:12.02,OP,,0,0,0,,michitarita hibi yori mo taritenai kurai ga ii
