Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.72,0:02:21.90,OP,,0,0,0,,Girls have fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.20,0:02:24.90,OP,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 100,0:00:20.09,0:00:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Chiar... am supraviețuit, nu-i așa?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:25.84,0:00:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hei... Cu tine vorbesc.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:28.66,0:00:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu nu sunt "tine".
Dialogue: 100,0:00:30.34,0:00:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Atunci, spune-mi numele tău.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:32.04,0:00:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Before asking someone's name,\Nyou should first introduce your—
Dialogue: 100,0:00:34.84,0:00:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, for crying out loud!\NThen let's do introductions.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:38.02,0:00:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ce?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:38.68,0:00:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go first.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:40.21,0:00:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu sunt Suzumori Asuka.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:41.70,0:00:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in Class C, and I'm on both the\Nbasketball team and the track team.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:46.11,0:00:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Încântată de cunoștință.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:47.40,0:00:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go next.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:49.19,0:00:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Kujou Shion from Class 2-B.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:51.89,0:00:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I like to play piano, and I have\Na dog named Arnold.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:57.08,0:00:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Pleased to meet you.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:58.37,0:00:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 100,0:00:59.98,0:01:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm from Class A. My name is Amatani Mutsu.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:03.23,0:01:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,My hobbies are reading and cooking... Oh!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:06.44,0:01:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And I've held on to the number one spot\Nin my class since I was a freshman!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:09.75,0:01:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, I've never been late once!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:12.01,0:01:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm confident in my ability\Nto memorize things!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:14.22,0:01:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I also know a lot about astronomy!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:16.28,0:01:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Really... Okay. Next.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:18.82,0:01:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Onishima Homare.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:20.52,0:01:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Class F.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:23.91,0:01:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? That's it?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:25.01,0:01:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have anything else?\NSomething to make people like you?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:28.54,0:01:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Something to make people like me?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:30.66,0:01:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if this counts, but...
Dialogue: 100,0:01:33.29,0:01:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Being stranded like this...
Dialogue: 100,0:01:36.03,0:01:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't my first time.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:39.66,0:01:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We're stranded?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:55.03,0:02:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Listen closely, Homare.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:57.17,0:02:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,When you face your opponent, make sure\Nto stand ready with your blade hidden.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:00.87,0:03:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Homare, you should never eat slugs raw.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:04.99,0:03:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Moose testicles are a rare and valuable\Ncut of meat that can be eaten raw.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:08.82,0:03:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't expect much in regard to flavor.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:13.15,0:03:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa...
Dialogue: 100,0:03:14.35,0:03:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,B*lls stink!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:17.05,0:03:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,B*lls stink!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:19.15,0:03:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa...
Dialogue: 100,0:03:20.71,0:03:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:22.09,0:03:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:23.30,0:03:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,B*lls?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:24.10,0:03:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:24.64,0:03:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! She's awake.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:25.91,0:03:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm fine...
Dialogue: 100,0:03:27.90,0:03:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,How is this fine? We got washed away!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:30.74,0:03:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a miracle we survived,
Dialogue: 100,0:03:33.49,0:03:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,but how long do we have to wait to be rescued?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:36.05,0:03:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm already dying of thirst.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:38.45,0:03:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we have lots of water, right?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:40.30,0:03:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't drink seawater.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:42.10,0:03:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Why?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:42.99,0:03:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Because there's salt in it.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:45.20,0:03:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll lose more moisture than you take in.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:49.11,0:03:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's say that a person\Nneeds two liters of water a day.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:52.67,0:03:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If you lose two percent of that, you get thirsty.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:55.25,0:03:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,At three percent, signs of dehydration start.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:57.74,0:03:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,At five percent, you get\N headaches and dizziness.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:59.97,0:04:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,At ten percent, organ function decreases...
Dialogue: 100,0:04:02.58,0:04:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,leading to death.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:04.30,0:04:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You really know a lot about this.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:08.09,0:04:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What's all this?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:10.31,0:04:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:11.52,0:04:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't be moving yet...
Dialogue: 100,0:04:19.82,0:04:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,A... A fish?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:21.32,0:04:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a flying fish.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:23.56,0:04:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:25.80,0:04:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not... Are you going to eat it?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:28.54,0:04:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What we need right now is moisture.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:30.49,0:04:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Digesting food uses a lot\N of moisture too, so...
Dialogue: 100,0:04:34.38,0:04:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's better not to eat for now.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:36.48,0:04:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Wrap it in fabric and crush it well...
Dialogue: 100,0:04:38.80,0:04:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,then when you squeeze it like this...
Dialogue: 100,0:04:45.99,0:04:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You can drink the bodily fluids, like the\Nmoisture from the organs and the blood.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:49.19,0:04:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Here. You should have some, too.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:53.20,0:04:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Really...?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:56.43,0:05:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,If there are flying fish...\Nthat means there's land nearby.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:01.06,0:05:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't see anything besides the horizon.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:04.91,0:05:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,When you're on the water, \Nthe horizon you see isn't very far away.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:08.40,0:05:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's probably about four\N or five kilometers ahead.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:10.95,0:05:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm amazed you can still wear that shirt.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:14.11,0:05:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The circumference of the Earth\Nis about 40,000 kilometers, so...
Dialogue: 100,0:05:17.88,0:05:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The radius would be about 6,400 kilometers.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:20.59,0:05:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If you put our view point\Nat just over one meter, then...
Dialogue: 100,0:05:24.17,0:05:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,According to the Pythagorean theorem...
Dialogue: 100,0:05:27.26,0:05:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true. What we're seeing is only\N about four or five kilometers away.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:31.90,0:05:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! You're super smart!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:33.99,0:05:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I shouldn't have expected\Nany less from someone wearing glasses!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:36.57,0:05:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Glasses have nothing to do with it.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:39.77,0:05:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget that, we need water! Water!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:42.03,0:05:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Unlike that fish juice girl,\Nthe rest of us are delicate!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:45.69,0:05:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,How thirsty are you?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:48.11,0:05:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm dying of thirst!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:50.02,0:05:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. All right, then.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:52.12,0:05:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:52.74,0:05:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Close your eyes, open your mouth,\N and lie down facing up.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:55.95,0:05:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:58.23,0:05:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,To help remove resistance to the idea.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:59.83,0:06:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:01.51,0:06:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,When it's fresh, it's sterile.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:03.64,0:06:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you guys doing?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:05.75,0:06:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I missed.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:06.67,0:06:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, please! Not that!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:09.29,0:06:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's better than dying, isn't it?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:10.47,0:06:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,She's still fine! Probably!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:12.31,0:06:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}But...
Dialogue: 100,0:06:12.31,0:06:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I have to keep waiting? Hurry up!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:15.97,0:06:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:23.41,0:06:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,A rescue team... never came for us.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:27.73,0:06:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Our one and only class trip is...
Dialogue: 100,0:06:30.71,0:06:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did it turn out like this?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:32.53,0:06:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,If nothing had gone wrong,\Nwe'd be in bed at the hotel right now.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:39.10,0:06:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Does anyone have any fun stories?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:44.34,0:06:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess not, right?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:59.49,0:07:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. Hey!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:04.65,0:07:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it morning?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:06.38,0:07:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You're finally awake.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:10.81,0:07:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I can see land.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:13.10,0:07:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:13.78,0:07:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Over there.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:16.97,0:07:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But with these currents,\N we're going to miss it.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:21.28,0:07:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Dying would be better than\Nhaving to stay here forever.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:24.36,0:07:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We have no choice but to swim.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:26.69,0:07:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the most reasonable choice.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:29.85,0:07:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,A tiger shark?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:31.42,0:07:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It couldn't be worse.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:33.22,0:07:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:34.55,0:07:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing. Just get swimming.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:41.10,0:07:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pretty far, isn't it?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:44.77,0:07:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a little further! Keep—
Dialogue: 100,0:07:48.53,0:07:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Sh...
Dialogue: 100,0:07:49.44,0:07:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Shark!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:52.95,0:07:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:13.00,0:08:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I kept using an old-style phone\Nin case of disasters, but...
Dialogue: 100,0:08:16.72,0:08:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, there's no helping it now.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:19.05,0:08:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Is everyone all right?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:22.10,0:08:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so scared...
Dialogue: 100,0:08:23.84,0:08:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't take any more.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:25.19,0:08:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the shark?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:26.18,0:08:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It swam off.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:27.82,0:08:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Sharks have special receptors\Nin their noses, the ampullae of Lorenzini,
Dialogue: 100,0:08:30.80,0:08:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,that can sense electricity.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:32.76,0:08:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You can deliver a pretty severe\Nshock using a cell phone battery.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:36.74,0:08:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's amazing you know that.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:40.06,0:08:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I learned from my father.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:42.57,0:08:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, is this place really safer... for us?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:49.69,0:08:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:53.72,0:08:56.50,top,,0,0,0,,Hey! We're not done with introductions!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:56.50,0:08:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, this isn't\Nthe first time you've been stranded?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:59.71,0:09:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:00.68,0:09:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Before, in the Pacific Ocean,\Nthe Atlantic Ocean, the Indian Ocean...
Dialogue: 100,0:09:03.74,0:09:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,While I was traveling with my father\Nwe ran into a few problems.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:07.31,0:09:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:08.37,0:09:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So... I guess you're sort of a pro\Nat getting stranded, Onishima-san.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:12.16,0:09:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What do we do now?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:14.01,0:09:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What is essential in a survival situation is—
Dialogue: 100,0:09:17.25,0:09:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Amatani-san! Are you all right?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:18.98,0:09:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to carry her to the shade, gently.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:23.70,0:09:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 100,0:09:25.21,0:09:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:26.42,0:09:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Her pulse is normal.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:28.33,0:09:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's most likely dehydration.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:30.65,0:09:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You should rest here\Nin the shade without moving.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:33.82,0:09:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,First, we need to find drinking water.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:36.54,0:09:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Please gather up any empty bottles\Nyou find washed up on the beach.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:39.77,0:09:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go, too.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:41.18,0:09:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I probably have the most\Nendurance of anyone here.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:43.93,0:09:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What's that about?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:45.45,0:09:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You two are going to look for water,\Nand we have to pick up trash?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:48.89,0:09:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,To secure large amounts of water,\Nwe will need receptacles.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:52.58,0:09:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And it would be best\Nif someone stayed with her.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:57.43,0:10:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,About finding water. Allow me\Nto give a simple explanation.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:00.63,0:10:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. Did you eat something just now?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:03.29,0:10:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,There are five ways to obtain drinking water.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:05.87,0:10:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,First, to take it from plants or animals.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:08.84,0:10:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You can get water from\Ncoconuts and cut banana trunks.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:13.07,0:10:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Though it doesn't seem like\Nthis island would have either.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:16.26,0:10:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You can get water by cutting\Nthe bamboo and vines
Dialogue: 100,0:10:18.49,0:10:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,that are more likely to be here, but...
Dialogue: 100,0:10:20.45,0:10:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,it takes a really long time.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:23.05,0:10:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The second way is to purify undrinkable water.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:25.69,0:10:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The third way is to distill seawater.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:28.27,0:10:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But we don't have the tools for either.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:30.58,0:10:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The fourth way is rain water, but...
Dialogue: 100,0:10:33.10,0:10:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't wait around for rain to fall.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:35.96,0:10:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The fifth way is to find a water source.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:38.49,0:10:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Given the size of this island,\Nthere should be a spring somewhere.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:43.37,0:10:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Just wait a little longer.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:45.14,0:10:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I've been feeling lightheaded for a while.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:48.79,0:10:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Collect your spit in your mouth\Nand breathe through your nose.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:52.25,0:10:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Nu mai am nici salivă în gură!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:02.07,0:11:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Nu-ți face griji. \NȚi-am dat puțină de la mine.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:05.35,0:11:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hei! Rezistă!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:07.68,0:11:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Homare...
Dialogue: 100,0:11:10.02,0:11:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,C-Ce... este asta?
Dialogue: 100,0:11:13.85,0:11:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:15.19,0:11:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Este un picior.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:16.18,0:11:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,De la lăcusta pe care am mâncat-o mai devreme.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:20.14,0:11:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Primul meu sărut... a avut gust de lăcustă.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:25.77,0:12:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Data viitoare, cazul 2:
Dialogue: 100,0:12:27.51,0:12:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,"Prima noastră masă."
